== 播出情况 ==
因2006年9月18日WB电视台与UPN电视台合并为CW电视台，本剧的第2季变为在[[CW电视台|CW电视台]]首播。之后各季也都在[[CW电视台|CW电视台]]首播。

== 评论与反响 ==
{{expand section|time=2016-3-19}}
《邪恶力量》第2季的评分较低。虽然CW电视台希望能吸引到更多成年人观众，但本季的主要收视人群为青少年女孩。<ref>{{cite news |title=TV Preview: 'Supernatural' tries to come out of the shadows |first=Rob |last=Owen |url=http://www.post-gazette.com/tv/2007/03/15/TV-Preview-Supernatural-tries-to-come-out-of-the-shadows/stories/200703150354 |publisher=''Pittsburgh Post-Gazette'' |language=en |date=March 15, 2007 |accessdate=September 14, 2009 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924152702/http://www.post-gazette.com/tv/2007/03/15/TV-Preview-Supernatural-tries-to-come-out-of-the-shadows/stories/200703150354 |dead-url=no }}</ref>它在[[电视联播网#美国|美国电视网]]黄金时段节目收视率榜中只排名第216位<ref name="s2ratings"/>，美国平均收视率约为3.14百万人次<ref name="s2ratings">{{cite web |title=Season Program Rankings |url=http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=052207_07 |publisher=ABC Medianet |language=en |date=May 22, 2007 |accessdate=September 14, 2009 |archive-date=2011-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110825010107/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=052207_07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，本剧能否续订一直到最后几集播出时都是很成问题的事情<ref name="doubt">{{cite web |title=Supernatural ratings less than super |last=McFarland |first=Melanie |url=http://www.startribune.com/entertainment/tv/11918311.html |publisher=''Seattle Post-Intelligencer'' |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080308165151/http://www.startribune.com/entertainment/tv/11918311.html |language=en |date=November 23, 2007 |accessdate=September 14, 2009 |archivedate=March 8, 2008}}</ref>。尽管收视率不乐观，制作方后来还是决定续订[[邪恶力量_(第三季)|新的一季]]。一位美国特种部队副军士长(Special Forces Soldier Master Sergeant)凯文·维斯(Kevin Wise)在2007年的《邪恶力量》见面会上曾提到在当时美军驻[[伊拉克|伊]]和驻[[阿富汗|阿]]士兵向总部征求的DVD消遣品中，请求数量最多的就是本剧的前2季。<ref>{{cite web |title='Supernatural' Stars Presented with Honorary Coin on Veteran's Day |first=Lisa |last=Claustro |url= http://www.buddytv.com/articles/supernatural/supernatural-stars-presented-w-13869.aspx |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5rzOIfmDE?url=http://www.buddytv.com/articles/supernatural/supernatural-stars-presented-w-13869.aspx |publisher=BuddyTV |language=en |date=November 17, 2007 |accessdate=November 26, 2009 |archivedate=August 15, 2010}}</ref>

